# =============================================================================
# ⚠️  DEVELOPMENT ONLY - Homeserver Admin Credentials
# =============================================================================
# ⚠️  WARNING: These variables are for LOCAL DEVELOPMENT and E2E TESTING ONLY!
# ⚠️  DO NOT SET THESE IN PRODUCTION - leave them unset/empty!
#
# These credentials are used to generate signup tokens during development.
# They are server-side only (no NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix) so they are NEVER
# exposed in the client bundle. The token generation happens via an API
# route at /api/dev/signup-token which is blocked in production.
#
# For production: Users should obtain invite codes through proper channels
# (SMS verification, payment, etc.) - NOT through admin token generation.
